sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Consumidor as Consumidore/Aplicación
    participant API as API Pago Prestamo Corresponsal Bancario <br> Epica 2267: PagoPrestamo <br> HU 57112:  POST - /correspondent-management/v1/execute-loan-repayment
    participant cloudWatch as AWS CloudWatch <br> Registro de logs
    participant CL as Caché Local
    participant Lambda as Lambda de <br> parámetros
    participant Lib as Librería Pipeline (ConfigMap)
    participant wrapper as Wrapper RegionDB <br/> HU 61083 - POST: /wrapper-region-db/v1/execute-procedure <br> SP: REGISTRA_TRANSACCION_CANAL
    participant lambdaSP as Lambda Validación Corresponsales<br/> HU 7761 - ban-xrs-ic-lam-validate-bank-correspondent-{env}
    participant execute as API Comp Pago Préstamo <br> Epica 2267: PagoPrestamo <br> HU 56993:  POST -  /loan-payment/v1/execution
    participant Errors as Control de Errores <br> <<Librería de mapeo de errores>>
    
    Note over Consumidor, Errors: Flujo Honduras (HN01) - Pago Prestamo Corresponsal Bancario

    Consumidor->>API: REST Request
    Note right of Consumidor: header: <br> soruceBank <br> branch-id <br> body: <br> correspondentLocationReference <br> correspondentSubLocationReference <br> loanId, <br> paymentTransactionAmount, <br> paymentTransactionCurrency, <br> paymentMechanismType, <br> debitAccountReference, <br> chequeInstrumentReference, <br> bankPartyReference, <br> externalInterfaceReference, <br> correspondentTransactionReference

    API->>API: Validar Request
    Note over API: Valida campos obligatorios según contrato OpenAPI 

    API->>cloudWatch: Registra log con request recibido

    API->>API: Validación exitosa

    alt Consulta parametros en caché local

        API->>CL: Consultar parámetros Lambda Parámetros caché local
        Note right of API: Domain: "CORRESPONDENT_MANAGEMENT" <br> name: "EXECUTE_LOAN_REPAYMENT" <br> country: XRS 

        CL->>API: Obtiene parámetros Lambda Parámetros Cahé Local
        Note left of CL: Obtiene parámetros de regionalización y negocio
 
    else Consulta  parametros en Lambda Parámetros / Parameter Store

        API->>Lambda: Consultar parámetros lambda parámetros
        Note right of API: Domain: "CORRESPONDENT_MANAGEMENT" <br> name: "EXECUTE_LOAN_REPAYMENT" <br> country: XRS 

        Lambda->>API: Obtiene parámetros Lambda Parámetros
        Note left of Lambda: Obtiene parámetros de regionalización y negocio

        API->>CL: Guarda parámetros lambda Parámetros en caché local
        Note right of API: value.param-name 

    end

    API->>API: Validar Servicio Regional
    Note over API: Usando parámetros de regionalización obtenidos

    API->>API: Validación Regional success
    Note over API: Servicio habilitado para HN01 

    API->>Lib: Consulta Constantes
    
    Lib->>API: Retorna constantes necesarias
    Note left of Lib: Constantes: <br> connectionType <br> operationType <br> catalogueName <br> packageName <br> procedureName

    API->>API: Construye request Wrapper RegionDB - SP: REGISTRA_TRANSACCION_CANAL
    Note over API: Mapeo: <br> connection: { <br> param-name = lambda.param-name <br> secret-name = lambda.secret-name <br> }, <br> connectionType = const.connectionType <br> operationType = const.operationType <br> catalogueName = const.catalogueName <br> packageName = const.packageName <br> procedureName = const.procedureName <br> params: { <br> PV_CORRESPONSAL = header.application-id <br> PN_TIPO_TRANSACCION = lambda.transactionTypeRegister <br> PV_CODIGO_CANAL = lambda.channelCode <br> PN_ESTADO_TRANSACCION = lambda.transactionState <br> PN_MONTO = request.paymentTransactionAmount <br> PV_MONEDA = request.paymentTransactionCurrency <br> PV_CODIGO_PAIS = header.sourceBank <br> PV_CLAVE_CORRESPONSAL = request.correspondentTransactionReference <br> PV_REFERENCIA_T24 = lambda.t24Reference <br> PV_CLAVE_TRANSACCION = request.loanId <br> PV_COD_CORRESPONSAL = header.branch-id <br> PV_PUNTO_VENTA_CORR = request.correspondentLocationReference <br> PV_SUB_PUNTO_VENTA_CORR = request.correspondentSubLocationReference <br> }

    API->>wrapper: Consume Wrapper RegionDB - SP: REGISTRA_TRANSACCION_CANAL
    Note right of API: Request: <br> connection: { <br> param-name, <br> secret-name }, <br> connectionType, <br> operationType, <br> catalogueName, <br> packageName, <br> procedureName, <br> params: { <br> PV_CORRESPONSAL, <br> PN_TIPO_TRANSACCION, <br> PV_CODIGO_CANAL, <br> PN_ESTADO_TRANSACCION, <br> PN_MONTO, <br> PV_MONEDA, <br> PV_CODIGO_PAIS, <br> PV_CLAVE_CORRESPONSAL, <br> PV_REFERENCIA_T24, <br> PV_CLAVE_TRANSACCION, <br> PV_COD_CORRESPONSAL, <br> PV_PUNTO_VENTA_CORR, <br> PV_SUB_PUNTO_VENTA_CORR <br> }

    wrapper->>API: Response Wrapper RegionDB - SP: REGISTRA_TRANSACCION_CANAL
    Note left of wrapper: Response: <br> success, <br> data

    API->>API: Evalúa response Wrapper

    alt If responseWrapper.data.outputParameters.PV_ERRORCODE != "SUCCESS"

        API->> Errors: Mapear código de error
        Note right of API: Mapeo de errores según tabla de homologación SP REGISTRA_TRANSACCION_CANAL
        
        Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado
        
        API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
        Note left of API: HTTP 4XX / 5XX

    else If responseWrapper.data.outputParameters.PV_ERRORCODE == "SUCCESS"

        API->>API: Construye request Lambda Valida Corresponsal
        Note over API: Mapeo: <br> branchId = header.branch-id, <br> country = request.header.soruceBank, <br> transactionType = lambda.transactionTypeValidate

        API->>lambdaSP: Consume Lambda Valida Corresponsal
        Note right of API: branchId, soruceBank, transactionType

        lambdaSP->>API: Response Lambda Valida Corresponsal
        Note left of lambdaSP: Response: <br> creditAccountReference, <br> debitAccountReference, <br> permittedCurrencyCode, <br> transactionType, <br> commissionAmount, <br> commissionCurrencyCode, <br> commissionTransactionType, <br> commissionAccountReference

        API->>API: Evalua response Lambda Valida Corresponsal

        alt If lambdaValCorr.success == false

            API->> Consumidor: Retorna error generado por la lambda
            Note left of API: HTTP 4XX / 5XX

        else If lambdaValCorr.success == true

            API->>API: Evalúa Moneda
            Note over API: request.paymentTransactionAmount == lambdaValCorr.permittedCurrencyCode

            alt If request.paymentTransactionAmount != lambdaValCorr.permittedCurrencyCode

                API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                Note left of API: HTTP 422: Moneda inválida para la transacción

            else If request.paymentTransactionAmount == lambdaValCorr.permittedCurrencyCode

                API->>API: Evalúa Método de Pago
                Note over API: paymentMechanismType == "CASH"

                alt If paymentMechanismType != "CASH"

                    API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                    Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                    API->> Consumidor: Retorna error
                    Note left of API: HTTP 422: Tipo de pago inválido
                
                else If paymentMechanismType == "CASH"

                    API->>API: Construye Request API executePayment
                    Note over API: Mapeo: headers <br> body: <br> loanId = request.loanId, <br> paymentAmount = request.paymentTransactionAmount, <br> paymentType = lambda.paymentType, <br> accountNumber = lambdaValCorr.debitAccountReference, <br> chequeNumber = request.chequeInstrumentReference, <br> bankCode = request.bankPartyReference, <br> interfaceReferenceNumber = request.externalInterfaceReference, <br> transactionReferenceBC = request.correspondentTransactionReference, <br> currencyCode = request.paymentTransactionCurrency

                    API->>execute: Consume API executePayment
                    Note right of API: loanId, paymentAmount, paymentType, <br> accountNumber, chequeNumber, bankCode, <br> interfaceReferenceNumber, transactionReferenceBC, currencyCode

                    execute->>API: Response API executePayment
                    Note over execute: Response: <br> paymentExecutionDateTime, loanId, installmentReference, paymentAmount

                    API->>API: Evalúa Response API executePayment

                    alt If data.success == true 

                        API->>API: Construye response API Experiencia
                        Note over API: Mapeo uno a uno con response API Composición executePayment

                        API->>Consumidor: Response Exitoso
                        Note left of API: HTTP 200: Response Body 

                    else If data.success == false 

                        API->> Consumidor: Retorna error generado por API Composición executePayment
                        Note left of API: HTTP 4XX / 5XX 

                    end

                end 
                
            end

        end

    end 

    Note over Consumidor, Errors: Flujo Alternativo - Error
    activate API
    alt Exception occurs
        note over Errors: Error Library Handler
        activate Errors
            API->> Errors: Mapear código de error
            Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado
        deactivate Errors
        activate Consumidor
            API-->> Consumidor: Retorna error
        deactivate Consumidor
        Note over Consumidor,Errors: Diagrama guía de manejo de errores <br> http://bit.ly/4rpKVIU
    end
    deactivate API